		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Good [4.17]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Zuranthium&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Okay when you are outdoors and want to get away from a MOB thats attacking you, you usually do what? RUN. However, most of the time you will die becuase the thing attacking you can run faster or just as fast. Here comes the trick that will save your life hundreds of times over when outdoors. While running hit the number lock button. This will make you run forward without holding the forward button. Then hold the CTRL key and one of the sideways moving buttons(lef or right). The effect? You will strafe WHILE running, making you move FASTER than most MOBS. <br /><br />If you don't have sow or aren't a bard, this will save you A LOT. It even helps if you DO have sow, becuase then you will be able to run faster than MOBS with sow speed. If you are able to cast sow and it runs out right when you are about to run away, this trick will save your life. <br /><br />Please give me some good ratings for this one. I just saved your life many times, no matter what kind of character you play. BTW, try not to spread it around too much. If everyone finds out Verant will fix it (YIKES). <br /><br />Corpusnuntia/Divineshadow/Zuranthium/Plantmaster/Naltec/Natalos/Sunsong <br /><br />Player of many characters on the Nameless server. <br /></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >2 Replies</td></tr></table>
